{"tid":2226406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日有黑警冇將頭頂cam嘅保護貼摵走就用","createTime":"2020-10-02T04:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T04:55:04.000Z","uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f315e7bfedc129c38e050d4fc8cba84405711569","tid":2226406,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSJCcJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSJCcJ4.jpg&h=23e06fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【🤭 塊膠貼擋住個鏡頭喎... 】<br />\n<br />\n昨日「10.1 國慶」，警方派出大批警員在銅鑼灣等區域執勤，並以涉嫌非法集結等罪名拘捕至少 80 人。昨日行動中，部分防暴警員的頭盔上配備了運動攝影機，不過警方在屏幕位置貼上編號貼紙，遮蔽新機鏡頭的膠貼亦未撕下。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者所見，警員配備的運動攝影機型號為內地品牌大疆創新（DJI）的 Osmo Action，香港官方價格 2,999 元。攝影機能夠拍攝 4K 影片，並且配備增強拍攝穩定程度的技術，即使拍攝時有追逐等動作，畫面都不會大幅搖晃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3515782728507322/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3515782728507322%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAs5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=54c63710\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3515782728507322/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8a65a91b2f4851210e3b9598a2024ed0ea5774","tid":2226406,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094c0291f0986cde2ced08f69dda754e66e338f1","tid":2226406,"uid":31863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"你估佢地真係好想戴住呀<br />\n阻住哂想打下市民都唔得"},{"pid":"3083838a5469a8a7d9f9c1a4beee80316da558de","tid":2226406,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"，唔讀書嘅垃圾係咁上下"},{"pid":"e3bc1ed03f23c451659533a86e9cef3f326d3820","tid":2226406,"uid":212260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc8a65a